{
  "page": "West way",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>west way</b> is a path between <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Standfast\" title=\"Standfast\">Standfast</a> in the north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The route crosses the <a href=\"/index.php/Chequy_Water\" title=\"Chequy Water\">Chequy Water</a> and passes through <a href=\"/index.php/Wat%27s_Wood\" title=\"Wat&#39;s Wood\">Wat's Wood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=West_way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Osgrey\" title=\"Eustace Osgrey\">Eustace Osgrey</a> buried his first wife and their sons beneath <a href=\"/index.php/Standfast\" title=\"Standfast\">Standfast</a>'s hill along the west way.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> and his squire, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a>, took the west way to <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a> when negotiating between Eustace and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=West_way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>We'll take the west way. It is little used these past years, but still the shortest way from <a href=\"/index.php/Standfast\" title=\"Standfast\">Standfast</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat Castle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Osgrey\" title=\"Eustace Osgrey\">Eustace Osgrey</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=West_way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Road\" title=\"Template:Road\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Road&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Road (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Road&amp;action=